Class UserHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.mage.sdk.datastore.DaoHelper<User>
      • mil.nga.giat.mage.sdk.datastore.user.UserHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDaoHelper<User>, IEventDispatcher<IEventEventListener>, IUserDispatcher

    public class UserHelper
extends DaoHelper<User>
implements IEventDispatcher<IEventEventListener>, IUserDispatcher
    A utility class for accessing User data from the physical data model. The details of ORM DAOs and Lazy Loading should not be exposed past this class.
